WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.070
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:05.550
joining me again tonight. I want to go

00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:08.590
over what the Lord showed me real fast

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:09.990
yesterday

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:11.790
about the towers. There was a lot the

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:14.430
Lord showed us yesterday, son.

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:19.230
I want to show you this article real

00:00:19.240 --> 00:00:22.150
quick from Russia and what they said

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:24.230
they want to do.

00:00:24.230 --> 00:00:24.240
It’s

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:28.230
interesting. I told you

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.430
Venezuela and Russia will become friends

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:33.310
in the days ahead. I've told you this

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:35.150
over and over again. I said

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:38.750
Venezuela will be handed a

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:40.750
lifeline

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:44.070
from Russia to join the BRICS—to join

00:00:44.080 --> 00:00:46.390
the superpowers of the world because of

00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:49.550
oil and Venezuela and the visions in the

00:00:49.560 --> 00:00:52.150
past. I said they

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:53.070
will

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:56.270
back Russia's oil reserves and the

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:58.510
things going on with Russia for their

00:00:58.520 --> 00:01:01.190
economy, and this would be an extension

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:04.310
to them. So we see

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:07.030
Russia saying today that they're

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:09.710
open to sending hypersonic missiles to

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:12.030
Venezuela.

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:16.590
I wonder why?

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.790
Well, because I told you in the visions

00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:21.870
yesterday that I saw that the

00:01:21.870 --> 00:01:21.880
Venezuelan

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:24.430
prime minister will

00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:26.910
end up being a Saddam Hussein, and it

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:29.310
will be like

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:31.750
it was in Iraq; it would be its type

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:33.470
and shadow.

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:39.190
I thought that was kind

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:40.630
of interesting.

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:43.390
So now we also see

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:46.310
that

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.550
election anxiety triggers a $100

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:52.230
million wave of NYC

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:52.240
buyers

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:54.510
heading south. People

00:01:54.520 --> 00:01:55.990
want to head south. People are

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.670
wanting to leave New York. And I told you

00:01:58.680 --> 00:02:02.390
what I saw. It wouldn't just be New York.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.870
In the days ahead, I saw Pennsylvania, I saw a

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:09.430
lot of upper East

00:02:09.430 --> 00:02:09.440
states—far

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:12.270
Northeast

00:02:12.270 --> 00:02:12.280
states—would

00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:15.070
start to migrate. The Christian families in those

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:17.390
states,

00:02:17.390 --> 00:02:17.400
and

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:19.590
non-Christians,

00:02:19.600 --> 00:02:23.630
trying to leave those areas saying, 'We

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:26.070
want to relocate. We're

00:02:26.070 --> 00:02:26.080
done.'And

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:29.190
so I saw a lot of that happening

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:31.870
over the next year or two, people

00:02:31.880 --> 00:02:33.670
trying to really

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.990
flee those areas

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:39.310
because of riots there and because of

00:02:39.320 --> 00:02:40.630
all the things that the Lord has showed

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:42.350
me. You know, I know we can stop a

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:43.750
lot of this through prayer. We're going

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:44.830
to pray,

00:02:44.840 --> 00:02:46.710
but I know that a lot of people are

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:48.150
wanting to seek

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:49.630
a

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:51.870
better opportunity for their families,

00:02:51.880 --> 00:02:53.630
especially in school districts and

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:56.190
liberals. And especially, isn't

00:02:56.200 --> 00:02:58.110
it interesting how that man came out so

00:02:58.120 --> 00:03:00.590
strong about who he really is?

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:02.350
And that's the reason for the title

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:04.830
of the video today: 'You'll get what you

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:06.110
asked for, but it's not what you

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:07.310
thought.'And

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:08.710
that's to

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:11.590
the people of New York. You'll get it. I

00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:13.750
saw him winning and I even saw him

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:16.830
standing in New York Times Square

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:19.310
as I saw the flash of light with the two

00:03:19.320 --> 00:03:22.110
men standing there from CNN,

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:24.190
and that

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:26.710
man was standing on stage

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:30.110
at the New Year's Eve thing.

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.190
I thought that was interesting

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:34.870
because I knew he'd win. I told Braden,

00:03:34.880 --> 00:03:36.710
'You know, even in the prophetic

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:39.230
words, I told you all I was saying that

00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:41.870
basically New York's in trouble.'And I

00:03:41.880 --> 00:03:46.270
saw what David Wilkerson had prophesied

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:48.150
was going to start to come to pass. The

00:03:48.160 --> 00:03:51.470
things that we have seen will start

00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:55.750
to pan out over the city of New York.

00:03:55.760 --> 00:03:58.510
A lot of people, it's going to be a

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:01.190
ground of great testing and shaking.

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:04.110
So, like I said, I

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:05.670
don't come on here trying to bring fear,

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:07.750
but I try to tell you what's coming and

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:10.310
what the Lord has showed us.

00:04:10.320 --> 00:04:13.670
I'm going to go over the

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:17.069
building that I saw, and it wasn't the

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:19.190
Hudson.

00:04:19.200 --> 00:04:21.990
In my mind, I only see the Hudson River

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.230
because I thought that was the only

00:04:23.240 --> 00:04:25.350
river, out of ignorance of what flows

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.510
through

00:04:26.520 --> 00:04:29.990
New York. But it's the East River.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:33.950
So in the vision last night,

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:37.870
I saw the East River, which my son said,

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:40.230
'The Hudson's over here, Daddy.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:42.390
The East River is right here.'So

00:04:42.390 --> 00:04:42.400
in

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:45.230
the vision, I'm seeing the East River,

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:47.230
and I called out the Hudson. So that's my

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:48.910
mistake. I'm

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:51.150
going to tell you that immediately.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:54.790
The East River is right here. I see

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:59.950
Central Park up here. I see the East

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:02.270
River and I see the building that's all

00:05:02.280 --> 00:05:03.910
glass.

00:05:05.760 --> 00:05:09.030
That was a strategic location for this

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:11.750
attack that I saw.

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:22.150
In between the

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.790
East

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:26.030
River

00:05:26.040 --> 00:05:28.070
and the garden

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:29.470
is

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:32.470
one of Trump's towers.

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:34.790
And

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:37.270
when I was looking at the building on

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:38.750
fire,

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:43.070
it was on the northeastern side.

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:44.950
The fire and the

00:05:44.960 --> 00:05:47.150
explosion exploded all the way around

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:49.190
and

00:05:49.190 --> 00:05:49.200
it

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:51.150
caught the whole thing.

00:05:51.160 --> 00:05:53.590
It looked like 9/11 with the plane,

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:55.310
but I don't know

00:05:55.320 --> 00:05:57.510
what caused the fire. I still don't, as

00:05:57.520 --> 00:05:59.710
I'm praying into this, but this is

00:05:59.720 --> 00:06:01.230
something that I want you to pray with

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:02.110
me

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:04.790
because I believe what the Lord

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:06.110
showed me:

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:09.470
I saw people on barges

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:12.550
shooting some kind of

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:14.990
rocket launcher or some kind of man-made

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:18.070
device at this building.

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:20.670
Well, this building is close enough to

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:23.110
that river;

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:25.430
it's right there. And as I was looking at

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:28.670
everything on fire up top, if you go

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.910
back to the prophetic word,

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:33.390
the word of the Lord said, 'This is a

00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:35.950
distraction. This is not the main

00:06:35.950 --> 00:06:35.960
event;

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:37.910
this is a distraction

00:06:37.920 --> 00:06:39.270
from what they're really going to try to

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:41.990
do.'And

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:44.310
as I was praying into this last

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.950
night,

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:48.110
the Lord showed

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:48.910
me—because

00:06:48.920 --> 00:06:50.670
I was asking him, 'Lord, show us

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:55.190
the date'—and he said, 'You ask a

00:06:55.190 --> 00:06:55.200
lot.'He

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:56.830
doesn't want me to share

00:06:56.840 --> 00:06:58.990
that kind of stuff on

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.870
YouTube.

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:02.470
So he

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:05.110
took me because he knows I love George

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:07.790
Washington Carver

00:07:07.790 --> 00:07:07.800
and

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:09.950
the book 'The Man Who Talks to

00:07:09.950 --> 00:07:09.960
the Flowers.'It's

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:12.470
one of my favorite books.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:19.270
George Washington Carver asked,

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:21.790
'Show me what's about the

00:07:21.790 --> 00:07:21.800
peanut.'He

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:23.550
goes, 'Go back

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:26.190
and ask smaller, simpler questions.

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:31.390
You're asking too much of a complex

00:07:33.230 --> 00:07:33.240
question.'He

00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:38.070
was

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:42.390
saying,

00:07:43.640 --> 00:07:45.190
'You need to

00:07:45.200 --> 00:07:46.790
think different.

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:48.430
Go at this a different way.'It was

00:07:48.440 --> 00:07:50.230
the way he talked to George

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:52.310
Washington Carver because I said, 'Lord, I

00:07:52.320 --> 00:07:55.150
want a deeper relationship with you.

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:57.470
I want

00:07:57.480 --> 00:07:59.790
to hear you more intimately.

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:03.270
I want to have more

00:08:10.710 --> 00:08:10.720
fellowship.'So

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:20.750
here we are.

00:08:20.760 --> 00:08:23.270
We're going to pray tonight.

00:08:23.280 --> 00:08:25.430
I pray about the buildings. I pray about

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:29.270
what I saw about

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:33.469
Japan and South Korea and the

00:08:33.479 --> 00:08:35.190
