00:09:55.550 --> 00:09:55.560
There

00:09:55.560 --> 00:09:57.710
are

00:09:57.710 --> 00:09:57.720
many

00:09:57.720 --> 00:10:00.910
avenues,

00:10:00.920 --> 00:10:02.990
in my opinion,

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:05.150
