It's what makes us drink.

00:51:08.720 --> 00:51:10.390
It's what draws them in and makes them

00:51:10.400 --> 00:51:12.670
drink. When you taste salty things, it

00:51:12.680 --> 00:51:14.990
makes you thirsty.

00:51:15.000 --> 00:51:16.630
"Come unto me all ye that are heavy

