00:52:15.440 --> 00:52:16.710
You say, "Well, I haven't seen that."Well,

00:52:16.710 --> 00:52:16.720
you've

00:52:16.720 --> 00:52:18.670
got to get on your face. What

00:52:18.670 --> 00:52:18.680
is

00:52:18.680 --> 00:52:21.630
Kathryn Kuhlman saying today

00:52:22.920 --> 00:52:24.710
about

00:52:24.720 --> 00:52:26.870
the one we listened to about prayer? Yes.

00:52:26.880 --> 00:52:28.870
She was talking about having a

00:52:28.880 --> 00:52:30.550
