00:52:30.560 --> 00:52:33.190
Him. But she said

00:52:33.200 --> 00:52:36.830
being quiet, learning

00:52:36.830 --> 00:52:36.840
to

00:52:36.840 --> 00:52:39.470
just be still. She said, "Be still and

00:52:39.470 --> 00:52:39.480
know,"as

00:52:39.480 --> 00:52:41.670
the scripture says. "Be still

00:52:41.680 --> 00:52:44.470
and know,"and don't "be still and don't know."Be

00:52:44.470 --> 00:52:44.480
still and

00:52:44.480 --> 00:52:45.510
know

00:52:47.680 --> 00:52:49.390
