00:53:59.120 --> 00:54:02.110
So we must learn to quiet our minds.

00:54:02.120 --> 00:54:04.470
Quiet. Be quiet.

00:54:04.480 --> 00:54:06.510
She said it a lot better than me.

00:54:06.520 --> 00:54:08.230
No, you said it good, baby.

00:54:08.240 --> 00:54:10.510
She was talking

00:54:10.520 --> 00:54:11.950
about how we're in a hurry to go

00:54:11.960 --> 00:54:13.950
