00:55:33.880 --> 00:55:36.550
Where you

00:55:36.560 --> 00:55:38.110
meet each other, where your

00:55:38.120 --> 00:55:40.550
will becomes His will.

00:55:42.200 --> 00:55:44.390
It's not just about you asking for

00:55:44.400 --> 00:55:46.510
